--
-- Setup Selenium locally --
--

# For Debian 8:

1.) Install nvm (node version manager) [https://github.com/creationix/nvm]:
    curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/creationix/nvm/v0.33.2/install.sh | bash

2.) Install npm (node package manager) with nvm:
    nvm install node

3.) Install protractor (AngularJS's wrapper for selenium):
    npm install -g protractor

4.) Run:
    webdriver-manager update
    
--
-- Setup Selenium server --
--

# For Debian 8 (TODO: some of the installs may not be needed, please prune):

1.) Download selenium server jar from http://docs.seleniumhq.org/download/
2.) Copy the jar file to the machine or VM that will act as the selenium server
3.) Install your webdrivers:
    - For Chromium:
    sudo apt-get install build-essential chromium default-jre default-jdk chromedriver
    ln -s /usr/lib/chromium/chromedriver /usr/bin/chromedriver

4). Install Oracle's Java8 (may work with other versions, be my guest):
    sudo apt-get install software-properties-common
    sudo add-apt-repository "deb http://ppa.launchpad.net/webupd8team/java/ubuntu xenial main"
    sudo apt-get update && sudo apt-get install oracle-java8-installer oracle-java8-set-default

5.) Cross fingers and attempt running the selenium hub server with:
    java -jar selenium-server-standalone-<version>.jar -role hub

6.) Add a node (or four) to the selenium hub with:
    java -jar selenium-server-standalone-<version>.jar -role node  -hub http://localhost:4444/grid/register

7.) If everything is working, add the selenium hub command to /etc/rc.local and start-up some nodes in a screen session?


--
-- Running angular tests with protractor on the test executor -- 
--

1.) Install the node package manager (npm); find instructions for your OS - good luck.
2.) Install protractor globally with `npm install -g protractor` (may require root/sudo)
3.) Configure a running selenium server.


--
-- Helpful resources --
--

1.) https://github.com/SeleniumHQ/selenium/wiki
2.) https://ramonvictor.github.io/protractor/slides/#/1
